      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "As Artemis II reaches for the moon, maritime dominance has never been so important.\n\nWith NASA’s launch of Artemis II heralding America’s return to crewed lunar exploration, the USCG was on station, executing our critical role in this national endeavor.\n\nIn seamless partnership with @NASA and interagency partners, our crews ensured the safety and security of the maritime domain, demonstrating our unique capability to support complex interagency missions.\n\nCongratulations to NASA and the crew of Artemis II on a successful launch!\n\nRead more here: https://t.co/6DueyPj5Ix\n\n@USCGSoutheast",
      "text_resolved": "As Artemis II reaches for the moon, maritime dominance has never been so important.\n\nWith NASA’s launch of Artemis II heralding America’s return to crewed lunar exploration, the USCG was on station, executing our critical role in this national endeavor.\n\nIn seamless partnership with @NASA and interagency partners, our crews ensured the safety and security of the maritime domain, demonstrating our unique capability to support complex interagency missions.\n\nCongratulations to NASA and the crew of Artemis II on a successful launch!\n\nRead more here: https://www.news.uscg.mil/Press-Releases/Article/4448013/coast-guard-partner-agencies-to-support-historic-artemis-ii-launch/\n\n@USCGSoutheast",
